Line1.F53E7: Ah, the witch of the tower. Yes, we are acquainted.
Line3.F53E7: I felt her absence from the swamps until only recently. She must have been sent a great distance to complete her task.
VoiceDir1.F53E7: Sly, amused but not giving anything away about your relationship.
VoiceDir3.F53E7: Sly. Perhaps you know more about this than you are letting on.
